Title: Primalist Fashion
Description:
Ah, $n, there you are!

The robes of the primalists make for interesting study for the local tailors. If you could retrieve some from the primalists assaulting the dream, I would be pleased, yes?

No rips or tears please. Blood stains optional. They can be washed out.
ObjectivesText: Collect 10 Intact Primalist Garb from the Emerald Dream.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Return to Cylania in the Emerald Dream.

Objectives.Text: Complete the events of "Enter the Dream"
